CustomField.description: This is used to move a case out of the current Omni queue to ensure that skills can be recalculated correctly on reassignment of case. This is used only in the scenario where an agent reassigns a case.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This is used to move a case out of the current Omni queue to ensure that skills can be recalculated correctly on reassignment of case. This is used only in the scenario where an agent reassigns a case.
CustomField.label: Temporary Reassignment Queue
